title: The Real Housewives Of New York City S06E15 Ten Gallon Spats WEB
description: The ladies are set to escape the city and venture into big sky country: Montana! After procuring a doctor's note, Aviva opts out of the trip due to a sudden horse allergy and asthma condition that nobody is buying. The ladies hit the ground running in Montana, strapping on their designer boots and hats before heading out on a real-life cattle drive.
